- Call at 3 sites: cooldown block (L1599), fast-path pre-cc_part (L1699), full-path pre-cc_part (L2071)
- CC cooldown: 14 calendar days; too_recent suppression for same-day threads
- cc_memory_indexer.py: indexes reply_all_cache.json → cc_memory.jsonl per thread
- Dry-run: _suggest_cc_from_memory returns use_cc unchanged (no live writes)
- Fix stray duplicate return in _get_name helper
